        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Livestock Regulatory Protection Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Environmental Protection Agency from issuing permits under the Clean Air Act for any carbon dioxide, nitrogen oxide, water vapor, or methane emissions resulting from biological processes associated with livestock production.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
